          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="about-section" id="about">
      <div class="about-container">
        <div class="about-title"><h2>About</h2></div>
        <div class="about-info">
          <p>
            I'm a Fullstack Web Developer passionate about building modern,
            responsive, and user-friendly web applications. Skilled in both
            frontend and backend development, I enjoy crafting digital solutions
            from scratch — from designing clean interfaces to connecting with
            databases and servers. My tech stack includes Node.js, Express.js,
            Nest Js, Typescript, MySQL, and Vue, and I'm constantly exploring
            new technologies to stay ahead of the curve. I also have a strong
            interest in minimal design and creating smooth user experiences.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="about-img">
          <img src="/assets/FOTO 2.jpg" alt="" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="table-container" id="portfolio">
      <div class="table-title">
        <h2>Portfolio</h2>
      </div>
      <a href="/page/new" class="add-button"
        >Add New <i class="bi bi-file-earmark-plus" style="font-size: 2rem"></i
      ></a>
      <table>
        <tr>
          <th class="text-center">No</th>
          <th class="text-center">Activity Name</th>
          <th class="text-center">Activity Time</th>
          <th class="text-center">Action</th>
        </tr>
        <% data.forEach((d, i) => { %>
        <tr>
          <td><%= i+1 %></td>
          <td><%= d.nama_kegiatan %></td>
          <td><%= d.waktu_kegiatan %></td>
          <td class="action-btn">
            <a href="/page/edit/<%= d.id_portofolio %>" class="btn-act btn-edit"
              >Edit</a
            >
            <form
              action="/page/delete/<%= d.id_portofolio %>"
              method="POST"
              class="d-inline"
            >
              <button type="submit" class="btn-act btn-del">Delete</button>
            </form>
          </td>
        </tr>

        <% }) %>
      </table>
    </div>

